                Hamilton&nbsp;</FONT>Tracked Changes: Navigating the=20
                Document-Format Anti-Pattern =
(15+5)&nbsp;</SPAN></LI></UL>
              <LI><SPAN style=3D"line-height: 1.6;"><B>12:30 - 13:30=20
              Lunch&nbsp;</B></SPAN></LI>
              <LI><SPAN style=3D"line-height: 1.6;"><B>13:30 - 15:00 =
Session II:=20
              Change Tracking&nbsp;</B></SPAN></LI>
              <UL>
                <LI><SPAN style=3D"line-height: 1.6;"><FONT =
color=3D"#3d85c6">Svante=20
